answers.answer: What is the range indicated on your lab results - low to high? And why were you tested?

question: I am 21 years old, recently I had blood work done for other medical issues, the bloodwork came back that I have high insulin. Does this mean I am diabetic, or what could this mean? My insulin value was 57.4. Is this a very high level?
title: High Insulin Level- Diabetes?
